data.name: XRDesignPanelFileName
data.value: Gets or sets the path (including the file name) where the report currently being edited in the Design Panel will be saved. A report definition is usually saved to a REPX file.

data.name: XRDesignPanelDesignerHostLoading
data.value: For internal use. Occurs when the host of the current XRDesignPanel instance starts loading.

data.name: XRDesignPanelDeactivated
data.value: For internal use. Occurs when the host of the given XRDesignPanel instance has been deactivated.

data.name: XRDesignPanelComponentRemoving
data.value: Occurs before any component can be removed from the designer host of the report being currently edited in the Design Panel.

data.name: XRDesignPanelComponentRemoved
data.value: Occurs after any component has been removed from the designer host of the report being currently edited in the Design Panel.

data.name: XRDesignPanelComponentChanged
data.value: Occurs when altering a property that belongs to any component in the designer host of the report currently being edited.

data.name: XRDesignPanelComponentAdding
data.value: Occurs before a component can be added to the designer host of the report currently being edited in the Design Panel.

data.name: XRDesignPanelComponentAdded
data.value: Occurs after a component has been added to the designer host of the report currently being edited in the Design Panel.

data.name: XRDesignPanelCommandStatusChanged
data.value: Occurs if the status of a menu command has been changed.

data.name: XRDesignPanelBorderStyle
data.value: Gets or sets the Design Panel's border style.

data.name: XRDesignPanelActivated
data.value: For internal use. Occurs when the host of the given XRDesignPanel instance has been activated.

data.name: XRDesignGroupAndSortXRDesignPanel

data.value: Gets or sets the editor which is used to specify a font name.

data.value: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to show the Description bar at the bottom of the Property Grid.

data.name: PropertyGridDockPanelShowCategories
data.value: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to show categories for the items in the Property Grid, or show them in alphabetical order.

data.name: FieldListDockPanelShowParametersNode
data.value: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to show the Parameters node for end-users in the Field List.

data.name: FieldListDockPanelShowNodeToolTips
data.value: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to show node tooltips for end-users, for the purpose of teaching them to use the Field List.
